  "detailed_description": "The award-winning <i><strong>Eagle Island</strong></i> is a roguelite action-platformer that offers a unique blend of falconry-inspired combat mechanics, procedurally generated levels, and challenging boss fights. Players can choose between the narrative-driven story or speed-runner-like rogue mode, mixing and matching 85 abilities to diversify their gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/1dd2a97239b2701335c5e7a2981e6797.poster.avif?t=1709580045\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/1dd2a97239b2701335c5e7a2981e6797.webm?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/1dd2a97239b2701335c5e7a2981e6797.mp4?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVER 85 ABILITIES & PROCEDURALLY-GENERATED LEVELS IN CLASSIC MODE</h2>\"Throw\" your owl companion into battle imbued with special abilities! Explore procedurally-generated worlds, set to a beautifully modernized pixel art aesthetic. Levels are also packed with secrets and areas to explore.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/0dd4448327aedf8c27267dcd1ca39da0.poster.avif?t=1709580045\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/0dd4448327aedf8c27267dcd1ca39da0.webm?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/0dd4448327aedf8c27267dcd1ca39da0.mp4?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MORE IN HANDCRAFTED TWIST MODE</h2>In Eagle Island TWIST, you'll experience 45 carefully crafted, retro-themed stages that can be traversed on a 16-bit era world map. TWIST offers even more content to an already well-rounded game, providing a range of mini-games to supplement Classic Mode's roguelite feel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/b468dbab661362fd5d94e2dd1ed909e7.poster.avif?t=1709580045\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/b468dbab661362fd5d94e2dd1ed909e7.webm?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/b468dbab661362fd5d94e2dd1ed909e7.mp4?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOADED WITH ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES</h2>There are over 18 accessibility settings that can be easily enabled--Such as: remappable controls, difficulty options, text visibility, high contrast, and toggles for flashing and screen shaking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/3d321994545e03be8237458939d8d53e.poster.avif?t=1709580045\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/3d321994545e03be8237458939d8d53e.webm?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/3d321994545e03be8237458939d8d53e.mp4?t=1709580045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
